name: farewell for the graveyard
description:
farewell is inevitable for living creature. many things that can force you to say goodbye for good things or bad.
i think that farewell is a necessary for us for rebound from our past and continuing life. honestly, i dont know what i want to say. i just want to burry my nightmare, suffering a lot cause i have a lot of issues, and bad habit. 
sometimes, i want to recall that worst nightmare just to learn about life and moving forward.
---------------------------------
this is my third NFT. im so glad that many people support each other and make alot of positive vibes in community.
just moving on, guys.
